profile:
We are a locally owned and operated family plumbing and gas fitting business. We offer residential , commercial services, construction and renovations; from Poly B repairs to furnaces, cross connection tests and BBQ gas lines to boilers. We do it all. 

We offer 100% FREE Estimates. {Even if you don't book with us, its ALWAYS free}


We hope you give us a chance to serve you. 

For Quotes email: info@dukesplumbing.ca
Regular Service Request call: (403)474-2257
Emergency & Urgent needs call or text: (403)690-7586 - If we are on the line we always respond within 5 minutes

profile: Wiehler Mechanical is Calgary's premier plumbing and HVAC contractor, serving Calgary, Airdrie, Cochrane and the surrounding area for over 40 years. We offer full service residential and light commercial Furnaces, Air conditioning, Plumbing, Hot Water Tanks, Boilers and all other forms of HVAC and plumbing. Our technicians are the best in the business and can get your job done right.
